api_list.name: /countries
api_list.description: Countries that Asos supports selling products
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://asos-data-feed.p.rapidapi.com/countries"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "asos-data-feed.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
